MEETS TOM HANKS.

04:58.458 --> 05:02.500
YEAH, AND ABOUT AS SEXY
AS A BUCKET, DAWSON.

05:02.500 --> 05:03.542
OK.

05:03.542 --> 05:06.542
NOW, DAVE FACHELLI,
THAT'S A LEADING MAN.

05:06.542 --> 05:07.542
EXCUSE ME?

05:07.542 --> 05:10.208
YEAH, HE'S LIKE DARK
AND BROODING AND...

05:10.208 --> 05:14.458
RAY LIOTTA MEETS--
SEWER RAT. NO WAY.

05:14.458 --> 05:16.625
I'M JUST SAYING HE'S GOT
A CERTAIN...APPEAL.

05:16.625 --> 05:19.625
I MEAN, PEOPLE DON'T
NECESSARILY GO TO THE MOVIES

05:19.625 --> 05:22.500
TO SEE THEIR KIND, SWEET,
NEXT DOOR NEIGHBOR.

05:22.500 --> 05:24.959
THEY GO TO SEE THAT
SLIGHTLY DANGEROUS GUY

05:24.959 --> 05:26.583
THAT THEY DESPERATELY
WANT TO SLEEP WITH,

05:26.583 --> 05:28.375
BUT NEVER WILL IN REAL LIFE.

05:28.375 --> 05:31.291
SEXY WILL ALWAYS
WIN OUT OVER NICE.

05:31.291 --> 05:34.583
I'M JUST SAYING THAT
EVERYBODY CASTS TOM HANKS,
YOU KNOW?

05:34.583 --> 05:37.625
TRY AND MAKE
A LESS OBVIOUS CHOICE.

05:37.625 --> 05:38.625
HEY, MOVIE AUDITIONS TODAY.

05:40.125 --> 05:43.417
[♪♪♪]

05:48.417 --> 05:49.750
[CLEARS THROAT]

05:49.750 --> 05:52.041
HEY! WHAT'S THIS?

05:52.041 --> 05:55.208
THE RESULTS OF
PACEY WITTER'S HIV TEST.

05:55.208 --> 05:57.166
YOU GOT TESTED?

05:57.166 --> 05:58.500
YOU TOLD ME TO.

05:58.500 --> 05:59.583
BUT YOU ARGUED WITH ME.

05:59.583 --> 06:01.375
ANDIE, I ALWAYS ARGUE
WITH YOU.

06:01.375 --> 06:02.708
IT DOESN'T MEAN
I DON'T LISTEN.

06:04.625 --> 06:05.750
AND...?

06:05.750 --> 06:06.583
AND IT'S NEGATIVE,

06:06.583 --> 06:08.792
WHICH IS POSITIVE
IN MY BOOK.

06:08.792 --> 06:11.500
CONGRATULATIONS.
I'M PROUD OF YOU.

06:11.500 --> 06:14.166
GETTING TESTED WAS...
VERY RESPONSIBLE OF YOU.

06:16.458 --> 06:19.750
JUST DON'T THINK THAT,
YOU KNOW, NOW THAT YOU
GOT TESTED THAT, UM...

06:19.750 --> 06:20.875
WE'RE GOING TO...

06:20.875 --> 06:23.458
YOU KNOW.

06:23.458 --> 06:25.208
WHAT?

06:25.208 --> 06:26.375
YOU KNOW.

06:26.375 --> 06:30.834
NO, ANDIE, I HAVE NO IDEA
WHAT YOU'RE TALKING ABOUT.

06:30.834 --> 06:34.375
OK, UM...YOU KNOW,
WE HAVEN'T BEEN VERY...

06:34.375 --> 06:35.708
PHYSICAL...OR ANYTHING.

06:35.708 --> 06:39.500
AND, UM...I'M NOT OPPOSED
TO US BECOMING MORE...

06:39.500 --> 06:41.083
INTIMATE, BUT I
JUST WANT YOU TO KNOW

06:41.083 --> 06:43.041
THAT EVERYTHING'S GOT ITS
PERFECT PLACE AND TIME, OK?

06:43.041 --> 06:44.375
I DIDN'T GET TESTED

06:44.375 --> 06:46.708
TO ENGAGE IN ANY
UNINHIBITED SCRUMPING
WITH YOU.

06:46.708 --> 06:48.417
I GOT TESTED FOR ME.

06:48.417 --> 06:49.875
I DON'T WANT TO JUMP
IN THE SACK WITH YOU.

06:49.875 --> 06:51.458
OH.

06:51.458 --> 06:53.458
WELL, WHY NOT EXACTLY?
I MEAN...

06:53.458 --> 06:55.208
DO YOU NOT FIND ME
ATTRACTIVE?

06:55.208 --> 06:57.667
OF COURSE I FIND YOU
ATTRACTIVE, ANDIE.

06:57.667 --> 06:59.458
BUT YOU DON'T WANT TO?

06:59.458 --> 07:01.917
DO YOU WANT TO?

07:01.917 --> 07:04.375
I ASKED YOU.

07:04.375 --> 07:06.041
WELL, I'M ASKING YOU
BACK.

07:06.041 --> 07:10.500
YOU FIRST.

07:10.500 --> 07:14.417
I'D LIKE TO SCRUMP WITH
YOU ANY DAY OF THE WEEK,

07:14.417 --> 07:16.583
BUT...WE'VE GOT ALL
THE TIME IN THE WORLD.

07:16.583 --> 07:18.708
THERE'S NO NEED TO RUSH
INTO ANYTHING.

07:18.708 --> 07:22.708
I KNOW. I HEAR YOU,
AND I CONCUR.

07:22.708 --> 07:24.708
WELL...GOOD.

07:24.708 --> 07:27.250
BUT IF IT WERE THE RIGHT
TIME AND PLACE,

07:27.250 --> 07:28.166
YOU WOULD WANT TO, RIGHT?

07:28.166 --> 07:30.417
OH, HELL, YES.

07:30.417 --> 07:32.625
OK. GOOD. TILL THEN.

07:35.583 --> 07:36.542
UNTIL.

07:40.959 --> 07:42.625
HEY.
HEY.

07:42.625 --> 07:43.083
MOVIE AUDITIONS.

07:43.083 --> 07:45.000
ART CLASS.

07:46.583 --> 07:49.458
I SEE YOU GRADUATED
FROM FRUIT BOWLS.

07:49.458 --> 07:52.458
WE'RE DOING LIFE
SKETCHING. NUDE MODELS.

07:52.458 --> 07:55.834
WE'RE SUPPOSED TO SEE
THE HUMAN FORM AS A MASS
OF LINES AND SHADOWS.

07:55.834 --> 07:58.041
REALLY?

07:58.041 --> 07:59.583
I'M WORKING ON IT.

07:59.583 --> 08:01.166
AND HE JUST POSES FOR YOU?

08:01.166 --> 08:02.000
YEAH.

08:02.000 --> 08:03.375
DO YOU FIND THAT
UNCOMFORTABLE?

