WITH SOME GUY COMPLETELY
IN THE BUFF

08:05.291 --> 08:07.125
RIGHT IN FRONT OF YOU?

08:07.125 --> 08:08.708
NO.

08:08.708 --> 08:09.708
DOES HE LIKE...

08:09.708 --> 08:11.625
