08:14.125 --> 08:16.000
NO, HE DOESN'T TALK,
DAWSON.

08:16.000 --> 08:17.291
HE'S A MODEL.
HE SITS THERE.

08:17.291 --> 08:19.750
HE JUST TAKES BREAKS
EVERY NOW AND THEN.

08:19.750 --> 08:22.708
