DOESN'T BLUSH?

08:22.708 --> 08:24.708
NO.

08:24.708 --> 08:27.792
NOT EVEN A LITTLE?

08:27.792 --> 08:28.291
MAYBE A LITTLE.

08:28.291 --> 08:29.667
JUST A LITTLE?

08:32.250 --> 08:33.582
OK, I'VE
BROKEN 12 PENCILS,

08:33.582 --> 08:35.750
