INTERESTED.

10:02.625 --> 10:04.542
WOW!

10:04.542 --> 10:06.083
DON'T LOOK.

10:06.083 --> 10:07.417
I'VE SEEN A NAKED GUY
BEFORE, JOEY.

10:07.417 --> 10:10.250
YEAH, BUT NOT DRAWN
WITH THE TALENT
OF A SECOND GRADER.

10:10.250 --> 10:11.875
TRUST ME. I'M DOING
YOUR EYES A FAVOR.

10:11.875 --> 10:13.750
COME ON. LET ME SEE.
LET ME SEE.

10:13.750 --> 10:16.667
WOW! IT'S GOOD USE
OF LIGHT AND DARK,

10:16.667 --> 10:18.291
ESPECIALLY AROUND THE SIDE.

10:18.291 --> 10:19.500
I MEAN, IT'S VERY DRAMATIC.

10:19.500 --> 10:20.166
SHADING'S EXCELLENT.

10:20.166 --> 10:22.375
REALLY?

10:22.375 --> 10:23.333
YEAH.

10:23.333 --> 10:24.708
THE LINES ARE STRONG.

10:24.708 --> 10:27.792
UH, EVERYTHING SEEMS TO...
BE IN PROPORTION.

10:27.792 --> 10:31.125
UH...THE REALNESS--

10:31.125 --> 10:32.333
OH! GOD, JOEY!

10:32.333 --> 10:36.667
I'M SORRY. I'M SORRY.
I'M SORRY.

10:36.667 --> 10:38.125
Joey:
I GOTTA GO.

10:38.125 --> 10:41.625
I CAN'T BELIEVE
YOU'RE SAYING THIS
AFTER ALL THESE YEARS

10:41.625 --> 10:44.458
OF HIDING BEHIND HIGHBROW
ANALYTICAL POSSUMING--

10:44.458 --> 10:46.291
Boy: I LOVE YOU.

10:46.291 --> 10:48.000
I KNOW IT'S NONSENSICAL.

10:48.000 --> 10:49.583
NONSENSICAL? IT'S INSANE!

10:49.583 --> 10:51.208
WE'VE KNOWN EACH OTHER
FOR 15 YEARS.

10:51.208 --> 10:53.375
SOMEWHERE IN THERE YOU
COULDN'T FIND THE TIME
TO FREUDIAN SLIP--

10:53.375 --> 10:57.375
SO MANY TIMES, BUT YOU
DON'T KNOW HOW LONG
I'VE WRESTLED INTERNALLY

10:57.375 --> 11:01.500
WITH THE PSYCHOLOGICAL
REPERCUSSIONS
OF MY FEELINGS--

11:01.500 --> 11:05.625
YOU DON'T KNOW HOW LONG
I'VE BEEN STRUGGLING
INTERNALLY

11:05.625 --> 11:07.792
WITH MY PSYCHOLOGICAL
REPRODUCTIONS--

11:07.792 --> 11:09.542
BUT MY HEART SAYS
SOMETHING DIFFERENT.

11:09.542 --> 11:13.375
THAT I SHOULD CONSIDER
THE UNEQUIVOCAL,
POSSIBLY DAMAGING,

11:13.375 --> 11:18.083
HIGHLY IRRATIONAL,
HYPNOTICALLY SCARRING
PROPOSITION OF...

11:18.083 --> 11:20.542
OF LOVING YOU BACK.

11:20.542 --> 11:22.875
COOL.

11:26.166 --> 11:28.291
[♪♪♪]

11:36.166 --> 11:36.834
LISTEN, I'M SORRY.

11:36.834 --> 11:39.750
UH...CAN YOU SAVE IT?

11:42.000 --> 11:42.959
OH, GOD.

11:42.959 --> 11:45.625
ALL RIGHT, LOOK.
I-I'M SORRY. I MEAN...

11:45.625 --> 11:47.083
CAN I DO ANYTHING? WHAT?

11:47.083 --> 11:49.500
THERE'S NOTHING YOU
CAN DO, JACK. IT'S DUE THURSDAY.

11:49.500 --> 11:51.208
I'M ALREADY
THE YOUNGEST AND LEAST-
EXPERIENCED IN THE CLASS,

11:51.208 --> 11:53.417
AND NOW I'M GOING TO SHOW UP
WITH AN INCOMPLETE ASSIGNMENT.

11:53.417 --> 11:55.750
CAN YOU REDRAW IT?

11:55.750 --> 11:57.959
NOT FROM MEMORY. I MEAN,
THIS IS A NUDE MAN, JACK.

11:57.959 --> 12:02.208
I CAN'T JUST RECALL IT
FROM THIN AIR.

12:02.208 --> 12:03.250
THE--THE POSE,

12:03.250 --> 12:06.417
THE COMPOSITION,
THE LIGHT, THE SHADOWS...

12:06.417 --> 12:08.583
I JUST CAN'T RECREATE THAT.

12:08.583 --> 12:11.291
UM...

12:11.291 --> 12:13.250
LET ME POSE FOR YOU.

12:13.250 --> 12:13.875
WHAT?

12:13.875 --> 12:15.375
YEAH. NO, I'M SERIOUS.

12:15.375 --> 12:16.792
LET ME POSE FOR YOU.
NO BIG DEAL.

12:16.792 --> 12:19.083
YOU WANT TO POSE FOR ME
NAKED?

12:19.083 --> 12:21.708
UH-HUH. YEAH.

12:21.708 --> 12:23.375
UH, LET ME
THINK ABOUT THAT.

12:23.375 --> 12:24.959
NO.

12:24.959 --> 12:26.875
Jack: WELL...

12:26.875 --> 12:29.792
OK, UH, UH, OK,
WHAT HAPPENS IF YOU
DON'T TURN IT IN?

12:29.792 --> 12:32.917
I GET AN "F," NOT
TO MENTION EMBARRASSMENT

12:32.917 --> 12:34.917
AND FEELINGS
OF TREMENDOUS INADEQUACY.

12:34.917 --> 12:36.417
THAT'S IT.
I'M POSING FOR YOU.

12:36.417 --> 12:38.000
NO, YOU'RE NOT.

12:38.000 --> 12:39.750
FREAKED ABOUT
SEEING ME NAKED?

12:39.750 --> 12:42.917
AH, THE "JOEY'S A PRUDE"
TACTIC. CLEVER, BUT WRONG.

12:42.917 --> 12:44.166
ALL RIGHT. WELL THEN,
WHAT IS IT?

12:44.166 --> 12:46.375
I MEAN, YOU SCARED
IT MIGHT GET SEXUAL
OR SOMETHING?

12:46.375 --> 12:49.792
YOU KNOW, BELIEVE IT
OR NOT, JACK,

12:49.792 --> 12:51.250
NOT EVERY MOMENT WITH YOU
IS SEXUALLY CHARGED.

12:51.250 --> 12:52.917
SORRY.

12:52.917 --> 12:55.417
WELL, THEN THERE
SHOULD BE NO PROBLEM.

12:55.417 --> 12:56.875
COME ON, LOOK,
I FEEL AWFUL ABOUT THIS.

12:56.875 --> 12:59.291
I DON'T WANT YOU FAILING
YOUR FIRST ART PROJECT
BECAUSE OF ME,

12:59.291 --> 13:00.458
SO LET ME HELP YOU.

13:00.458 --> 13:01.875
YOU'RE SERIOUS,
AREN'T YOU?

13:01.875 --> 13:03.125
I'M DEAD SERIOUS.

13:03.125 --> 13:04.917
I HAVE HUGE GUILT
ABOUT THINGS LIKE THIS.

13:04.917 --> 13:07.417
SO DON'T FEEL WEIRD
'CAUSE I DON'T.

13:08.500 --> 13:10.166
I DON'T KNOW, JACK.

13:10.166 --> 13:11.583
I DON'T THINK THIS
IS A GOOD THING FOR US.
I MEAN WE SHOULD--

13:11.583 --> 13:14.041
STRICTLY
PROFESSIONAL, OK?

13:14.041 --> 13:16.166
I MEAN, COME ON, JOEY,
THIS IS YOUR ART.

13:17.583 --> 13:19.041
WELL...

13:19.041 --> 13:21.542
I GUESS THE MALE FORM
IS JUST THE MALE FORM.

13:21.542 --> 13:22.625
GOOD. IT'S SETTLED.

13:22.625 --> 13:24.708
I'LL BE BY YOUR HOUSE
TOMORROW AROUND 7:00.

13:27.291 --> 13:28.458
YEAH.

13:28.458 --> 13:30.708
WH--

13:40.750 --> 13:43.125
[♪♪♪]

13:50.208 --> 13:50.625
Man: THERE YOU GO, MISS.

13:50.625 --> 13:52.458
THANK YOU.

13:52.458 --> 13:55.375
CAREFUL OF THE DOSAGE.
I PUT A PAMPHLET IN THERE
FOR YOU.

13:55.375 --> 13:58.166
